GitHubApiData.name: laravel-multipayment-gateways
GitHubApiData.description: A Laravel Package that makes implementation of multiple payment Gateways such as Paystack, Flutterwave and Stripe endpoints and webhooks seamless.

TranslatedDescriptions.ja: Paystack、Flutterwave、Stripeなどの複数の決済ゲートウェイのエンドポイントおよびウェブフックの実装をシームレスにするLaravelパッケージ。
TranslatedDescriptions.zh-CN: 一个 Laravel 包，实现多种支付网关（如 Paystack、Flutterwave 和 Stripe）的端点和 webhook 的无缝集成。
TranslatedDescriptions.ko: Paystack, Flutterwave, Stripe 등의 여러 결제 게이트웨이 엔드포인트와 웹훅 구현을 원활하게 해주는 Laravel 패키지입니다.
TranslatedDescriptions.en: A Laravel package that facilitates seamless integration of multiple payment gateways such as Paystack, Flutterwave, and Stripe endpoints and webhooks.
TranslatedDescriptions.fr: Un package Laravel qui facilite l'implémentation de plusieurs passerelles de paiement telles que Paystack, Flutterwave et Stripe, ainsi que leurs points de terminaison et webhooks.
TranslatedDescriptions.es: Un paquete de Laravel que facilita la implementación de múltiples pasarelas de pago como Paystack, Flutterwave y Stripe, incluyendo endpoints y webhooks de forma sencilla.
